Quickstrike:




Quickstrike finally came to a stop as he came to the exact 
coordinates Black Arachnia gave him. He looked around, caution now 
seeping in. Dark Mouse did mention about a trap, but it couldn't be. 
He did think something was going on. 

He twitched with anxiety and looked back. He didn't see Dark Mouse. 
She must have not caught up with him yet. He thought she would have. 

He looked at the formation, his crimson optics glowing brightly.
